ze-full wp-post-image" alt="信心人 X 面料。图片来源：鲁本·巴斯蒂安·刘易斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Confidence-Man-X-Fabric.-Credit-Reuben-Bastienne-Lewis.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Confidence-Man-X-Fabric.-Credit-Reuben-Bastienne-Lewis-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Confidence-Man-X-Fabric.-Credit-Reuben-Bastienne-Lewis-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Confidence-Man-X-Fabric.-Credit-Reuben-Bastienne-Lewis-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Confidence-Man-X-Fabric.-Credit-Reuben-Bastienne-Lewis-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Confidence-Man-X-Fabric.-Credit-Reuben-Bastienne-Lewis-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Confidence-Man">Confidence Man</a>宣布了他们新的“Fabric Presents...”混音，并分享了他们的新单曲“Break It Down (On The Bassline)”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/confidence-man-glastonbury-2024-xcx-remix-new-album-3am-la-la-la-3770797">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的自信者：“我们处于音乐剧、艺术和彻底浪费之间”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支澳大利亚乐队与澳大利亚 DJ/制作人二人组 IN2STELLAR 合作制作了《Break It Down (On The Bassline)》，这是一首充满活力、脉动的舞曲，其中 Confidence Man 的 Janet Planet 在节目开始前演唱了<em>“Break it down on the bassline”。</em>低音下降。</p><p>他们与电子音乐文化的标志性中心 Fabric 合作推出了《Fabric Presents Confidence Man》，乐队在新闻稿中将其描述为“我们在派对和 DJ 中播放的一堆歌曲”。集等与一堆我们喜爱多年的老曲子相结合。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="BREAK IT DOWN (ON THE BASSLINE) (壮举. Janet Planet)" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fHhx_3xLUOI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他们继续说道：“还有我们也挖掘的朋友发来的一堆音乐。我们正在尝试制作一些我们喜欢跳舞的东西。”对于今天的合作，IN2STELLAR 补充道：“我们与 Confidence Man 一起度过了无数个夜晚的派对/夜店时光，并且始终因我们对 2000 年代早期俱乐部音乐和 DJ 的共同热爱而紧密相连。对我们来说，这首歌感觉就像所有一起出去的夜晚都融为一体，绝对是俱乐部的一首！！”</p><p> 《Fabric Presents Confidence Man》将于 8 月 23 日上映。您可以<a href="https://toastpress.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=4e1e2dbf318b66a015b7b5f9f&amp;id=3c0356e1ed&amp;e=b7b3c46261" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预购/预存</a>。单曲和混音都是乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-confidence-man-pull-massive-crowd-for-other-stage-performance-3769712">于 6 月 28 日下午在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024 的 The Other Stage 演出后制作的</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3773376" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3773376" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3773376" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="“织物呈现自信男人”艺术品。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Fabric-Presents-Confidence-man-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3773376" class="wp-caption-text"> “织物呈现自信男人”艺术品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“Fabric Presents Confidence Man”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p><strong>自信者——“让他们的钟声响起”*</strong><br /> <strong>Leinad——“电气城”</strong><br /><strong>约翰·海